high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the bath tub before turning right to face the toilet.
Take the roll of toilet paper on top of the toilet, next to the soap dispenser.
Turn around and walk across the room
Open the drawer on the left and place the roll of toilet paper inside.
Turn around and walk back across the room to the toilet.
Take the roll of toilet paper on the left side of the top of the toilet.
Turn around and walk across the room.
Open the drawer on the left and place the roll of toilet paper inside the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To take the toilet paper on top of the toilet and place it in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the toilet and face it.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper in the middle on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and approach the black cabinet under the sink.
Open the bottom left drawer and put the toilet paper in and then shut the drawer.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper.
Turn around and face the black cabinet under the sink.
Open the bottom left drawer and put the toilet paper in and then shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two rolls of toilet paper in a drawer under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees, walk to the bath tub, then turn right 90 degrees to face the toilet.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper that is on the back of the toilet in between the soap dispenser and the other roll of toilet paper.
Turn around 180 degrees, keeping the bath tub on the right hand side, and walk towards the sink.
Open the drawer on the left that is underneath the sink, place the roll of toilet paper inside the drawer in the front left corner (near you), and close the drawer.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk back to the toilet.
Pick up the other roll of toilet paper on the back of the toilet on the left hand side.
Turn around 180 degrees, keeping the bath tub on the right hand side, and walk towards the sink.
Open the drawer on the left that is underneath the sink, place the roll of toilet paper inside the drawer directly behind (away from you) the other roll of toilet paper, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two rolls of toilet paper into a drawer underneath the sink.
